WEBVTT

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:30.656
I had to admit that it looks like
there is some evidence

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:34.016
that marijuana can offer medical benefits

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:37.696
and I suggested that if she
really was interested,

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:39.240
she should try it.

00:01:39.800 --> 00:01:41.000
You know what she said?

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:45.600
This 73-year-old,
retired English professor?

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:48.616
She said, "I did try it
about six months ago.

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:50.176
It was amazing.

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:52.896
I've been using it every day since.

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:55.176
It's the best drug I've discovered.

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:59.336
I don't know why it took me 73 years
to discover this stuff. It's amazing."

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:00.376
(Laughter)